  Variables:
    caps_ref        (str)  CAPS reference e.g. "4.M.1.1"
    grade           (int)  Grade level e.g. 4
    term            (int)  CAPS term 1-4
    subject         (str)  Subject name e.g. "Mathematics"
    topic           (str)  Topic e.g. "Whole Numbers"
    subtopic        (str)  Subtopic e.g. "Ordering and Comparing 4-digit Numbers"
    objectives      (list) 1-3 measurable learning objectives
    difficulty      (str)  "foundational" | "developing" | "on_level" | "extending"
